_:Na8d2dec6e1c5405cbd4ca298edce0f26 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Ni allwn ateb galwadau oddi wrth unigolion am geisiadau am fudd-dal neu bensiwn. Dylech <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/cysylltu-canolfan-byd-gwaith\" class=\"govuk-link\">gysylltu â‘r Ganolfan Byd Gwaith</a> neu <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-pension-service\" class=\"govuk-link\">gysylltu â‘r Gwasanaeth Pensiwn</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"ymholiadau-cyfryngau-cenedlaethol-a-lleol-gan-gynnwys-cymru-ar-alban\">Ymholiadau cyfryngau cenedlaethol a lleol, gan gynnwys Cymru a’r Alban</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Swyddfa’r Wasg yr Adran Gwaith a Phensiynau</strong><br>\nCaxton House<br>\nTothill Street<br>\nLondon<br>\nSW1H 9NA <br>\nE-bost: <a href=\"mailto:newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Dilynwch ni ar Twitter <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.twitter.com/dwppressoffice\" class=\"govuk-link\">www.twitter.com/dwppressoffice</a></p>\n</div>" .
